{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_2__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 2, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 109, "language_hint": "en", "text": "This generic 12 step approach is applicable to all\norganisations, regardless of their size, type or industry."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_3__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 3, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 139, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Secure the backing you need to successfully\nimplement ISO 27001 by gaining the endorsement\nand commitment of your organization's leadership"}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_4__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 4, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 157, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Define the boundaries of your ISO 27001\nimplementation by identifying the parts of your\norganization, the information, and the systems that\nwill be included."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_5__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 5, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 83, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Identify gaps between the current and the desired\nstate of your security programme."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_6__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 6, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 169, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Establish a strong foundation for your information\nsecurity management system by creating a policy\nthat outlines your organization's security objectives\nand commitments."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_7__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 7, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 172, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Enhance your information security by assessing,\ndeveloping, and documenting the competence of\npersonnel, ensuring they meet the necessary security\nstandards and objectives."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_8__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 8, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 138, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Get a clear view of what needs to be protected by\ncataloging all the information assets within the\nscope of your ISO 27001 implementation."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_9__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 9, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 174, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Choose a risk management methodology that fits\nyour organization, ensuring you can effectively\nidentify and evaluate the security risks that threaten\nyour information assets."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_10__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 10, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 141, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Gain insight into the potential threats and\nvulnerabilities facing your information assets, and\nassess their potential impact and likelihood."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_11__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 11, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 171, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Decide on the best approach to manage each\nidentified risk, whether it's reducing, retaining,\ntransferring, or avoiding it, and then put the\nappropriate controls in place."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_12__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 12, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 172, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Continuously monitor and measure your information\nsecurity management system's performance to\nensure it's effectively managing risks and achieving\nyour security objectives."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_13__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 13, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 148, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Keep your information security management system\nup-to-date and resilient by continually identifying\nand implementing opportunities for improvement."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_14__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 14, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 173, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Validate your efforts and demonstrate your\norganization's commitment to information security\nby successfully undergoing an external audit to\nachieve ISO 27001 certification."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_15__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 15, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "char_count": 133, "language_hint": "en", "text": "THANKS FOR READING!\nLaunch, grow and accelerate your career\nin GRC in just 5 minutes per week. \nJoin 7,000+ subscribers at\ngrclab.com"}
